					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Wonderful containment procedures in terms of making the reader intrigued. This line especially is great.</p> <blockquote> <p>Footage of SCP-4317's feeding time is to be edited into an engaging compilation and posted on the official SCP-4317 YouTube page.</p> </blockquote> <p>And the rest of the article certainly did not disappoint. And having not read 1437, I feel this article works quite well on its own.</p> 
				 	]]>
