				<wikidot:authorName>aismallard</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4598089</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>After originally reading SCP-1437 a long while back, I really appreciated how perverse the alternate Foundations felt. Here, I really love how you demonstrate organizational priorities and their corporate disregard for human life. Lots of small word choices and sentence constructions that are absolutely fantastic throughout this.</p> <p>Can't wait for the Our Masters Above one. +1</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
